name: saasservicemgmt
ruby-cloud-description: SaaS Runtime lets you store, host, manage, and monitor software as a service (SaaS) applications on Google Cloud. Note that google-cloud-saas_platform-saas_service_mgmt-v1beta1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-saas_platform-saas_service_mgmt instead. See the readme for more details.
